 against the last known state stored in memory/heartbeat-state.json.\n\n**If nothing has changed since the last report:**\n- Stay SILENT. Send nothing. Not even HEARTBEAT_OK. Just exit quietly.\n\n**If there IS a change** (new session spawned, session died, agent failed, blocker appeared, task completed), compose a concise change report to group -5163901258:\n\nFormat:\n🟡 Orbis — 5p Update | {HH:MM} UTC {DD MMM}\n\nChanges detected:\n• [list of actual changes]\n\nPipeline: {HEALTHY if no failures / DEGRADED if failures}\n• Active sessions: N\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\n• Blockers: none / [list blockers]\n\nOnly send when something changed. Stay silent when stable.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 - 4:25 PM (UTC) / 2026-04-14 16:25 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1776183923006,"__openclaw":{"id":"a14193e5","seq":1}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the current state of sessions and compare against the stored heartbeat state."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l8lvoitaup40_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"limit":20,"messageLimit":2}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_l8lvoitaup40_2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/memory/heartbeat-state.json"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":438,"output":97,"totalTokens":14479,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776183923210,"responseId":"062d9d74685b0a4fa7b04068aead8904","__openclaw":{"id":"2c3eb1e5","seq":2}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","label":"Cron: 5p