its work and terminated. Now I'm comparing the running sessions across the baseline and current time to see if there's been any meaningful change in the active processes. The key finding is that telegram:direct:6053576134 shifted from running to done, but that happened at 16:15 UTC—the exact moment the baseline was recorded—so it's not a new state change. Everything else is matching the baseline, which means nothing has actually shifted. I should stay silent."},{"type":"text","text":"Comparing current state (16:22 UTC) against baseline from `heartbeat-state.json` (16:15 UTC):\n\n**Baseline:**\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d` ✅ running\n- `cron:6f3323ef` ✅ running  \n- `cron:e7885813` ✅ running\n- `main` ✅ done\n- Zombies: cron:b653a6c0, cron:ac986a8d, subagent:8bffa95f\n\n**Current:**\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d` ✅ running (no change)\n- `cron:6f3323ef` ✅ running (no change)\n- `cron:e7885813` ✅ running (no change)\n- `main` ✅ done (no change)\n- All zombies unchanged\n\nNo state transitions, no failures, no blockers detected since the 16:15 baseline.\n\nHEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":299,"output":619,"totalTokens":45298,"cacheRead":14264,"cacheWrite":30116,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776183791535,"responseId":"062d9cf01810e5804f661a5a9d42e761","__openclaw":{"id":"ceb9495a","seq":7}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","origin":{"provider":"telegram","accountId":"main_bot"},"displayName":"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-telegram-direct-6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram","to":"telegram:6053576134","accountId":"main_bot"},"updatedAt":1776183664707,"sessionId":"8e18daec-1780-455f-b7c4-896849ef86be","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":153035,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776162044660,"endedAt":1776162158012,"runtimeMs":113352,"childSessions":["agent:master-orch