eline exactly — same statuses, no failures, no blockers, no new sessions, no zombies changed.\nSystem: \nSystem: **No state transitions detected. Pipeline: HEALTHY. Silent.**\nSystem: [2026-04-14 15:53:00 UTC] State stable vs baseline. Silent.\nSystem: [2026-04-14 15:55:14 UTC] **Pipeline: HEALTHY. Silent.**\nSystem: [2026-04-14 15:59:42 UTC] Silent. All sessions match baseline — no new failures, no blockers, no state transitions since 15:30 UTC.\nSystem: [2026-04-14 16:02:56 UTC] Silent. All sessions match baseline — no new failures, no blockers, no state transitions since last check.\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/master-orchestrator/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 - 4:04 PM (UTC) / 2026-04-14 16:04 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776182742293,"__openclaw":{"id":"179949c4","seq":128}},{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Pipeline fully stable. No changes needed."},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":1100,"output":17,"totalTokens":77115,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":75998,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776182743254,"responseId":"062d98d9b6e825d6abd05492fcca3660","__openclaw":{"id":"b8cfca5f","seq":129}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:b653a6c0-143b-4b53-a242-034bc5fd9fca","kind":"other","channel":"unknown","label":"Cron: Orbis QLHV Report 11:53 UTC","displayName":"Cron: Orbis QLHV Report 11:53 UTC","updatedAt":1776167853466,"sessionId":"2f8d61ea-217f-4a52-8c6b-32e142e69caf","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"systemSent":true,"transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/2f8d61ea-217f-4a52-8c6